Package oracle.iam.identity.dbs.service.reconciliation.openfire

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AccountReconciliation
    The AccountReconciliation acts as the service end point for Identity Manager to reconcile account information from a openfire™ Database Service Provider.
    DeleteReconciliation
    The DeleteReconciliation acts as the service end point for Identity Manager to reconcile deleted account information from a openfire™ Database Service Provider.
    LookupReconciliation
    The LookupReconciliation acts as the service end point for Identity Manager to reconcile metadata information from a openfire™ Database Service Provider.
    Service
    The Service acts as the service end point for the Oracle Identity Manager to reconcile account information from a openfire™ Database Service Provider.
